  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the therapeutic effects of green tea extract on acne
      treatment and related hormone peptides by a double-blinded, randomized and controlled
      clinical trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      change in acne lesions counts, hormone, quality of life
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
